{"word":"G3973 - παύω - paúō - pow'-o - Cease","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pow'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cease</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முடி, நில், அமர், ஓய்ந்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to make to cease or desist: to restrain refrain"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primn. verb (&ldquo;pause&rdquo;); to <i>stop</i> (transitive or intransitive), that is, <i>restrain</i>, <i>quit</i>, <i>desist</i>, <i>come to an end:</i> - cease, leave, refrain.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}